          <h3 style="color:blue;">EMBROIDERY</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: 0%">The highly advanced Tajima machine with 20 heads makes it easy for us to craft the finest embroidery designs.

                The embroidery division is equipped with the latest machines from TAJIMA-(Japan Make).These automated embroidery machines elegantly handle any design with Punching ,Designing & Applique Cutting.</p>
            <h3 style="color:blue">GARMENTING</h3>
